    <summary>Self-hosted bot detection with 31 detectors, session vectors, and zero PII. Free forever.</summary>
    <description>StyloBot is a self-hosted bot defense proxy. Free forever.

31 detectors, sub-millisecond inference, 129-dimensional session vectors, intent classification, and reverse-proxy integration. One binary. No cloud dependency. Your traffic never leaves your perimeter.

## Quick Start
```
stylobot 5080 http://localhost:3000
stylobot 5080 http://localhost:3000 --policy block
stylobot start 5080 http://localhost:3000 --tunnel
stylobot man
```

## Features
- Sub-millisecond fast path detection (less than 1ms)
- 129-dim session vectors (Markov chains)
- LLM enrichment (OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, Groq, Ollama - any provider)
- Protocol fingerprinting (JA3/JA4, p0f, HTTP/2, QUIC)
- Real-time Spectre.Console live detection table
- Cloudflare Tunnel support (--tunnel)
- Background daemon mode (start/stop/status/logs)
- Zero PII architecture
    </description>
